snippet.textDisplay: Wasn't Coke Studio claiming to give a tribute to Aamir Zaki? This is just a collaboration, he was never invited to sing for Coke Studio, why? It's acceptable in Rohail Hyatt's seasons as he excluded Aamir Zaki when there was a demand to distribute money equaly in the days when he was being a part of Vital signs. But in Strings seasons from 7-10 he should've been given a chance even for once to sing, I respect them for that they invited him to play his parts but seemingly those aren't considered very enough for a talent who'd served for so long & when it required all his efforts & hardworks to be known. I wish he was given a chance to sing even for once along with his instrument playings, his reality saddened him a lot, if he would see such an offer in his time, he'd be happy, he wouldn't be that sad & malencholic as he looked all his life .. I was waiting, that Coke Studio will be accumulating his songs & doing something prolific in his memory, but still I see no one's paying a good sense of tribute to late Aamir Zaki, our legend's gone & even in a clear way CS's one member isn't between them & I see no response, it's something dull, I feel sorry. Not in this season but please if you could, procure some Aamir Zaki's tunes in the next season & present a ravishing rendition vocally as well, we're really gonna be thankful for that.
snippet.textOriginal: Wasn't Coke Studio claiming to give a tribute to Aamir Zaki? This is just a collaboration, he was never invited to sing for Coke Studio, why? It's acceptable in Rohail Hyatt's seasons as he excluded Aamir Zaki when there was a demand to distribute money equaly in the days when he was being a part of Vital signs. But in Strings seasons from 7-10 he should've been given a chance even for once to sing, I respect them for that they invited him to play his parts but seemingly those aren't considered very enough for a talent who'd served for so long & when it required all his efforts & hardworks to be known. I wish he was given a chance to sing even for once along with his instrument playings, his reality saddened him a lot, if he would see such an offer in his time, he'd be happy, he wouldn't be that sad & malencholic as he looked all his life .. I was waiting, that Coke Studio will be accumulating his songs & doing something prolific in his memory, but still I see no one's paying a good sense of tribute to late Aamir Zaki, our legend's gone & even in a clear way CS's one member isn't between them & I see no response, it's something dull, I feel sorry. Not in this season but please if you could, procure some Aamir Zaki's tunes in the next season & present a ravishing rendition vocally as well, we're really gonna be thankful for that.
